---
title: Crushed Peppercorn Steak with Creamed Kale and Potato Wedges
description: Although there’s a wide world of food to explore, sometimes you just wanna stick to the classics. We get it. But to make a tried-and-true recipe dazzle, you’ve got to maximize the power of your ingredients. Which is why we’re adding a sauce made with freshly cracked peppercorns to this steak and potatoes dish; crushing those ’corns by hand releases their essential oils and adds incredible depth.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c489c0ac445fa44e622c422-fccbab64.jpg
